Package: roc
Type: Package
Title: R tools for ocean colour.
Version: 0.0.8
Author: Michael D. Sumner
Maintainer: Michael D. Sumner<mdsumner@gmail.com>
Description: Work with data from NASA's Ocean Colour project, primarily the Level-3 bin files. Access
  to the HDF4 L3 bin files is via rrshdf4. 
License: GPL-3
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: dplyr
Imports:
    geosphere,
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.2),
    sp,
    raadtools,
    raster,
    rgdal
Suggests:
    rrshdf, 
    testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
NeedsCompilation: yes
